metadata.description:
collection created about what we expect for the future of the metaverse and the NFTs, the purpose of this collection is to achieve what we all live and expect about the constant change and the way we interact with the digital world.

Each NFT is unique, based on 100 modeled elements that define the "metaverse future man" as an extremely rare and rarely seen character.
